<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dim">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen">
    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/'}) %>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-24">
        <div class="hero min-h-[400px] bg-base-300 rounded-lg my-8">
            <div class="hero-content text-center">
                <div class="max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Welcome</h1>
                    <p class="text-xl mb-2"><%= studentName %> - <%= studentId %></p>
                    <p class="mb-8">Browse our current collection of modern solutions to help fight Climate Change.</p>
                    <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="card bg-base-300 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/img_01.jpg" alt="Abandoned Farmland" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
                    <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-300 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/img_02.jpg" alt="Alternative Cement" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
                    <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-300 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/img_03.jpg" alt="Bicycle Infrastructure" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
                    <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
                        <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary">More Information</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>